Package: overshiny
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Overlays on Shiny Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Nick", "Davies",
      email = "nicholas.davies@lshtm.ac.uk",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")
    )
  )
Description: `overshiny` provides draggable and resizable rectangular elements 
    that overlay plots in Shiny apps. This may be useful in applications where 
    users need to mark regions on the plot for further input or processing.
